channel.title: The number (Approved ++ works - Davidude36)
channel.description:
Yeah I was looking through deltascape off-topic section and I found this number, it's a help number or something for runescape..? 19856552500 i want to get my account unbanned because other people said they got theirs unbanned to.. _____________________________________________ I want to call it, but it might be a hoax. :) has anybody ever heard of this?
the topic : Hey Guys! My friend recently got into a big problem with JaGeX. He got his problem settled.
He was told to call this number through a Message on Runescape. He called it and a guy with a what seems to be Australian accent picked up. And spoke with him with a good mood and was a polite and fun person to talk to.
So I'm just asking if you'd call them. Its 100% Free too call. No charges it doesn't do anything wrong. If you have a problem then they will try to solve it for you and if you don't and just want to talk. They will ask questions Runescape based and talk friendly and such. I just called. Got back a account that was banned. It was a level 3 though lol XD..
So yeah. Just call this number. It's 100% Free. No charge.
19856552500
Make sure you call. It's quiet worth the shot. Thanks guys. _________________
Wow, this helped me so much, thanks! _________________
I'll call and ask them to upload all their models to uppit.com and tell me the url. :) lol
_________________
Hopefully this could help un-ban my pure ranger. _________________
Maybe it'll help me get my ollldd acc back _________________
w00t megasxlr36 unbanned germn boi29 unbanned well going to be i hope :) lvl105 and lvl88 :) :) :) _________________
ok i might not call it cause like... they could see where i live and st00ph but if i want to i might
_________________
Are you sure this isint some scam thing lol _________________
Lol, its not a scam. Don't worry. Its all legit buisness. _________________
How do we know this though? _________________
mean Jagex/Runescape are English so if they had a call center don't you think the receptionist would be English not Australian, Something weird with this. _________________
I just called it and it rang .. Then went to the voicemail lol.. its like someone cell phone.."You have reached the voicebox of ( whatever the number was) _________________
You double posted :\
But yeah. Its not like companies can't have people working in other places.
Its legit don't worry. There's nothing wrong at all. Just because it's a English company. Doesn't mean they can't have different races :P. _________________
